data.description: **BACK ON THE MARKET, buyer could not perform** Welcome to this charming MOTHER/DAUGHTER, nestled on a corner lot within a quiet cul de sac, located in one of the best areas in Union, NJ, the Battle Hill section! On the first floor (in-law Suite) you will find a Living Room, two Bedrooms, Eat in Kitchen, Full Bath and Laundry/Utility Room. On the second floor (Main Level) you will find a Living Room, Dining Room, Kitchen, two Full Baths, three Bedrooms and a stackable washer/dryer. The main living area boasts an open layout, perfect quality time. It includes a fully equipped kitchen, a comfortable living area, two dedicated bedrooms, and a full bathroom. This in-law suite allows for privacy while still being connected to the main residence.Upstairs, you'll discover the master bedroom with an en-suite bathroom, complete with ample closet space for added convenience. Two more well-sized bedrooms and another full bathroom ensure that everyone has their own space.Outside, the property sits on a generous corner lot, providing a large yard for outdoor activities. Including a spacious gazebo perfect for outdoor entertainment purposes. The cul de sac setting offers a safe and quiet neighborhood environment. You'll also find a private driveway and attached garage for parking convenience.This home benefits from its proximity to local amenities, shopping centers, dining options, and excellent schools.  Being sold AS IS
